 Golden Visa Program, officially known as the Cyprus Permanent Residency Program, allows non-EU nationals to obtain permanent residency through investment. It\u2019s either real estate, with a minimum requirement of \u20ac300,000. Applicants must also demonstrate a stable annual income from abroad and meet additional requirements including health insurance and a clean criminal record. The visa includes dependents ad immediate family, spouse and children under the age of 25, Cyprus Golden Visa is offering a route to live, study, and travel freely within Cyprus and, to some Schengen states.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-719a0793 e-grid e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"719a0793\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-48633c17 ekit-equal-height-disable elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"48633c17\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/eng.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <